data.synopsis:
After ten years, cousins Ken and Tomo—now with a matured body—reunite during the holidays. They hit it off and commit the forbidden act, but little do they realize that it was observed by Ken's devilish little sister, and the lengths that she'll go to to prevent their love from blooming further...

(Source: Irodori Comics)
data.background: Kyonyuu Itoko ga Iru Kyuuka was published digitally in English as Holiday with My Busty Cousin by Irodori Comics.
